            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_472wh' title='Col. 472WH &mdash; HC Deb 26 May 2004 vol 421 c472WH' name='column_472wh' href='#column_472wh' rel='bookmark'>472WH</a>
            Executive suggested? Does she also agree that that demonstrates what a great success the portable antiquities scheme has been in England and Wales? The Government should ensure its long-term funding, and that funding should be ring-fenced to ensure continued delivery of the project's aims.
