      <span class='time published'><a href="#2004-05-26T14:52:00Z" name="2004-05-26T14:52:00Z"><abbr class="dtstart" title="2004-05-26T14:52:00Z">2.52 pm</abbr></a></span>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0421P1_20040526_WH_61'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-hugh-bayley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0421P1_20040526_WH_61' title='Link to this speech by Mr Hugh Bayley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
